{"tid":2346150,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"終於要來了嗎？YG娛樂：「BLACKPINK成員ROSÉ、LISA即將發行SOLO曲，正在準備拍攝MV」","createTime":"2020-12-30T05:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T14:57:13.000Z","uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc074bbebd128051a36f8e1908b626ec3e69388","tid":2346150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_f2cc36f5d279944a1b0baef15ffc55bc/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-30/132656-891031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_f2cc36f5d279944a1b0baef15ffc55bc%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-30%2F132656-891031.jpg&h=2c74067c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日（30日），YG娛樂方面表示：「BLACKPINK成員ROS&Eacute;、LISA正在準備發行SOLO曲，正在準備拍攝MV。」<br />\n<br />\n還提到：「JISOO因為電視劇《雪滴花》拍攝日程，所以計劃在兩名成員之後發行SOLO曲，詳細的日程將在事後通過公告告知大家。」<br />\n<br />\nJENNIE在2018年11月發行SOLO曲《SOLO》，在各國榜單都獲得優異的成績，YG更曾多次提到其他成員正在準備SOLO曲。終於又有新消息，讓不少粉絲：「終於要來了嗎」、「兩年前就這麼說了」、「YG要說到做到」、「好期待」、「出了預告我才相信」等等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，BLACKPINK原訂在12月27日舉行線上演唱會《THE SHOW》，延期到明年1月31日。YG也表示：「為了一直等待的粉絲們，我們會更加努力準備，以更好的舞台和大家見面。」成員們目前都在為演唱會做準備。"},{"pid":"c8a7178fbb6b37055201592a28048e97035889b6","tid":2346150,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdf5f9fc231f1fb1e764fc4736d24ccea9262a2","tid":2346150,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c8a7178fbb6b37055201592a28048e97035889b6","tid":2346150,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:19:28.000Z","msg":"wow<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},